    • Method Detail

      • appendFilter

        public final B appendFilter(BusFilter<E> filter)
        Adds the given filter to the builder.

        The order of appending the filters to the builder is the order of the filters in the resulting bus.

        Parameters:
        filter - the filter to append

      • filters

        public final java.util.Deque<BusFilter<E>> filters()
        Obtains the filters added to this this builder by the time of the call.
        See Also:
        BusBuilder.appendFilter(BusFilter)

      • addListener

        public final B addListener(java.util.function.Consumer<E> listener)
        Adds a listener of the message posted to the bus being build.

        When a message is posted to the bus, the listeners are notified before invoking filters.

        If an exception is thrown by a listener code, it will be ignored by the bus.

      • removeListener

        public final B removeListener(java.util.function.Consumer<E> listener)
        Removes the listener. If the listener was not added before, the method has no effect.

      • listeners
